{"calories":"760","carbs":96,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eChef Shanna has a lot of love for a summer pasta salad, but knows it’s a recipe worthy of an update. Here, she tosses short, spiral-shaped rotini with sautéed zucchini, summer squash, and cherry tomatoes. Instead of a tangy dressing, a luxurious garlic mascarpone sauce coats every noodle.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eOne of our easy, family-friendly recipes for summer","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"376bfa307b","fat":30,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/hero_Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/menu_small_Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/small_square_Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/medium_square_Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51610/recipe_profile_page_Os7YlNfQHQouUgSzwSPg_1834_HEROES12086___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51613/large_cropped_eJbSFyyySJGmjMXPtBXx_1834_HEROES12086___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51612/eohBlvIUTtG889uIu1rO_1834_HEROES12083___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51612/menu_small_eohBlvIUTtG889uIu1rO_1834_HEROES12083___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/51611/Cw0NAX80RYG4RQgfslO1_1834_HEROES12087___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}}],"name":"Summer Vegetable Pasta with Mascarpone and Parmesan","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":26,"public_slug":"4p-lemony-cucumber-pasta-salad","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/33442/recipe_card20180726-11-1laooip.pdf","recipe_id":5285,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Summer Vegetable Pasta","subtitle":"with Mascarpone and Parmesan","title":"Summer Vegetable Pasta","legal_copy_short":"One of our easy, family-friendly recipes for summer","available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you\u0026#x27;ll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile it cooks, pasta releases starches into the boiling water. Adding some reserved pasta water to the sauce will help it cling to the noodles. It’s easiest to reserve this water in a liquid measuring cup, if you have one.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eSautéing the garlic after the vegetables have started cooking ensures it won\u0026#x27;t burn before they\u0026#x27;re tender. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat to do with the remaining mascarpone? Stir into a sauce for extra richness, spread over toast, or serve with fruit for a snack.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","12\" large high-sided pan"],"id":5285,"ingredients":["zucchini","summer squash","roasted red peppers","garlic","cherry tomatoes","rotini","unsalted butter","basil","mascarpone cheese","grated Parmesan cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"zucchini","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/97/medium_square_ZUCCHINI_copy.jpg"},{"name":"summer squash","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/500/medium_square_SUMMER_SQUASH_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"roasted red peppers","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2063/medium_square_2017-09-14___DS_17431250.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"cherry tomatoes","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/6/medium_square_cherry-tomatoes-test.jpg"},{"name":"rotini","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2370/medium_square_ROTINI_copy.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2371/medium_square_medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1276/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"mascarpone cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1501/medium_square_MASCARPONE_CHEESE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2309/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52390/recipe_card_size_Vx7xGCF4S4mHue17JxJy_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eBring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse all produce. Halve \u003cstrong\u003ezucchini \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003esummer squash\u003c/strong\u003e lengthwise; cut crosswise into .25-inch half-moons, discarding ends. Roughly chop \u003cstrong\u003eroasted red peppers\u003c/strong\u003e. Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté vegetables","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52391/recipe_card_size_iGcR9qDLSyW2aMTI4i51_2._Saute_Vegetables.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003ein a large high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003ezucchini\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e summer squash\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e whole cherry tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e. Sauté, stirring, until lightly browned and softened, about 5 minutes. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook rotini","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52392/recipe_card_size_7IKMu9FxS5CvKh5VJiE9_3._Cook_Rotini.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile vegetables cook, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003erotini \u003c/strong\u003eand cook until al dente, 7 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain and return to pot, off heat (see recipe tip). Add \u003cstrong\u003e1 packet\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e to rotini and toss to coat—this is a great task for a friend. Set aside until Step 5.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52393/recipe_card_size_htXEoZsRRAuaJDd5pv5o_4._Make_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile rotini cooks, roughly chop or tear \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems (a friend can also do this part). Push \u003cstrong\u003evegetables\u003c/strong\u003e to edges of pan, still over medium-high heat. Add \u003cstrong\u003eremaining\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e to center of pan. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e and sauté until fragrant, 2 minutes (see recipe tip). Remove pan from heat. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of mascarpone\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of basil\u003c/strong\u003e (see recipe tip). Set aside until rotini is cooked.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toss summer vegetable pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52394/recipe_card_size_UtARKeTLQPysSvLCkUGw_5._Toss_Vegetable_Pasta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce rotini is cooked, add \u003cstrong\u003eroasted red peppers\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003evegetables and sauce\u003c/strong\u003e to pot and toss to combine. Adding 1 tablespoon at a time, stir in \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e until sauce is silky and clings to pasta (you likely won\u0026#x27;t need to use all of the water). Taste and add \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate summer vegetable pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/52395/recipe_card_size_MPBKSk9TbKgZ4WKoIaz9_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide\u003cstrong\u003e summer vegetable pasta \u003c/strong\u003ebetween serving bowls. Garnish with\u003cstrong\u003e remaining basil \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in! \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""}],"feature":[{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"}]}}